#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmagnifier; is a screen magnifier by the KDE community. It can be used to "
"magnify a part of the screen. This application can be useful to various "
"people: People with low vision can use this application to magnify a part of "
"the screen which they are unable to view clearly, artists can use this "
"application to zoom into the graphics they produce and verify it at the "
"pixel level, image-processing researchers can use this application to zoom "
"into images and study them closely. Other than these, &kmagnifier; can be "
"used for various other purposes &eg; is possible to use the application for "
"grabbing a portion of the screen and saving it to the disk (with an option "
"of zooming the screen captured)."
msgstr ""
"&kmagnifier; je zaslonska lupa skupnosti KDE. Z njim lahko povečate del "
"zaslona. Ta aplikacija je lahko koristna za različne ljudi: slabovidni jo "
"lahko uporabijo za povečanje dela zaslona, ki ga ne morejo jasno videti, "
"umetniki lahko s to aplikacijo povečajo grafiko, ki jo ustvarijo, in jo "
"preverijo na ravni pikslov, raziskovalci, ki obdelujejo slike, pa jo lahko "
"uporabijo za povečanje slik in njihovo natančno preučevanje. Poleg tega "
"lahko &kmagnifier; uporabljate za različne druge namene &eg; aplikacijo "
"lahko uporabite za zajem dela zaslona in ga shranite na disk (z možnostjo "
"povečave zajete slike)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmagnifier; is a very powerful application with new features being added "
"all the time. It is optimized for use on low processing power machines."
msgstr ""
"&kmagnifier; je zelo zmogljiva aplikacija, ki ji ves čas dodajamo nove "
"funkcije. Optimizirana je za uporabo v računalnikih z nizko procesorsko "
"močjo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kmagnifier;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kmagnifier;"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screen shot of &kmagnifier;"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona za &kmagnifier;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screen shot of &kmagnifier;"
msgstr "Zaslonski posnetek &kmagnifier;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After running &kmagnifier; you will get a window similar to the one show "
"above. The main window of &kmagnifier; shows the magnified (or zoomed) "
"contents. We refer to this window as the <quote>zoom window</quote>. The "
"zoomed image shown inside the zoom window is captured from a part of the "
"screen. The part of the screen which is magnified is referred to as the "
"<quote>selection window</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete &kmagnifier; se prikaže okno, podobno tistemu, ki je prikazano "
"zgoraj. V glavnem oknu programa &kmagnifier; je prikazana povečana (ali "
"povečana) vsebina. To okno imenujemo <quote>okno povečave</quote>. Povečana "
"slika, prikazana v oknu povečave, je zajeta z dela zaslona. Del zaslona, ki "
"je povečan, se imenuje <quote>izbirno okno</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, &kmagnifier; magnifies the region around the mouse cursor into "
"the zoom window (think of it as a moving lens). Alternatively, you can ask "
"&kmagnifier; to magnify an chosen area of the screen (<guilabel>Selection "
"Window Mode</guilabel>) or the whole screen (<guilabel>Whole Screen Mode</"
"guilabel>) into the zoom window."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto &kmagnifier; poveča območje okoli kazalca miške v okno povečave "
"(predstavljajte si ga kot premikajočo se lečo). Druga možnost je, da v oknu "
"povečave zahtevate &kmagnifier; za povečavo izbranega območja zaslona "
"(<guilabel>Način izbire okna</guilabel>) ali celotnega zaslona "
"(<guilabel>Način celotnega zaslona</guilabel>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you would prefer not to see the mouse cursor in the zoomed image, select "
"<guilabel>Hide Mouse Cursor</guilabel>. Please note that &kmagnifier; cannot "
"yet find out the current cursor shape. Thus, it shows the default cursor."
msgstr ""
"Če na povečani sliki raje ne želite videti kazalke miške, izberite "
"<guilabel>Skrij kazalko miške</guilabel>. Upoštevajte, da s funkcijo "
"&kmagnifier; še ni mogoče ugotoviti trenutne oblike kazalke. Tako se prikaže "
"privzeta kazalka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing the part of the screen to be magnified"
msgstr "Spreminjanje dela zaslona, ki se poveča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When in <guilabel>Selection Window Mode</guilabel>, the zoom window and the "
"selection window can be moved and resized using the &LMB; like any window. "
"You can also change the position and size of the selection window using the "
"arrow keys on the keyboard, or by clicking into the zoom window:"
msgstr ""
"V načinu <guilabel>Način izbire okna</guilabel> lahko okno povečave in okno "
"izbire premikate in spreminjate njegovo velikost z uporabo &LMB; tako kot "
"vsako drugo okno. Položaj in velikost okna za izbiro lahko spreminjate tudi "
"s puščičnimi tipkami na tipkovnici ali s klikom v okno povečave:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>Arrow keys</keycap>, &LMB; or &MMB;"
msgstr "<keycap>Arrow keys</keycap>, &LMB; ali &MMB;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By keeping the &LMB; or &MMB; pressed in the zoom window and moving the "
"mouse, you can move the selection window. You can also use the arrow keys if "
"the selection window has the focus."
msgstr ""
"Če v oknu povečave držite pritisnjeno tipko &LMB; ali &MMB; in premikate "
"miško, lahko premikate okno za izbiro. Če je okno za izbiro v fokusu, lahko "
"uporabite tudi puščične tipke."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Arrow Keys</keycap></keycombo> or <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<mousebutton>&LMB;</mousebutton></keycombo>"
msgstr ""
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Arrow Keys</keycap></keycombo> ali <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<mousebutton>&LMB;</mousebutton></keycombo>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By using this combination, you can resize the selection window. Keep in mind "
"that the top-left corner of the selection window is kept constant and the "
"bottom-right corner is movable."
msgstr ""
"S to kombinacijo lahko spremenite velikost okna za izbiro. Upoštevajte, da "
"je levi zgornji kot okna za izbiro konstanten, desni spodnji kot pa je "
"premičen."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "More &kmagnifier; features"
msgstr "Več &kmagnifier; funkcij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmagnifier; comes with lots of features. It is possible to print the zoomed "
"image directly to a printer, save the image to a file, copy the zoomed image "
"to the clipboard (which can be used later to paste in other applications), "
"rotate the magnification image and more."
msgstr ""
"&kmagnifier; ima veliko funkcij. Povečano sliko lahko natisnete neposredno "
"na tiskalnik, shranite v datoteko, kopirate povečano sliko v odložišče (ki "
"jo lahko pozneje prilepite v druge aplikacije), obračate povečano sliko in "
"še več."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menus and Shortcuts"
msgstr "Meni in bližnjice"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Reference"
msgstr "Sklic na meni"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
